"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932450-Keely-Hodgkinson-Team-GB-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Keely Hodgkinson has clinched Team GB's12th gold medalof theParis Olympicsafter winning the 800 metres on Monday evening.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old won silver at the Tokyo Games three years ago and was the overwhelming favourite to win the 800m this year.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She raced away in the closing stages to cruise to victory as she clocked a time of 1:56.72 minutes.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The silver medal went to Ethiopia's Tsige Duguma, who ran a personal best time, with Kenya's Mary Moraa taking the bronze.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999873092665816, \"rank\": 1.2061227332172574e-05, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}, {\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999987867370775, \"rank\": 9.031696294196816e-07, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.8697035455545121, \"rank\": 0.09099170522031387, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the race, tributes poured in for Hodgkinson, who has been tipped to be a star of athletics for years to come.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.975952389098343, \"rank\": 0.024640147583305745, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The silver queen has stepped up to gold and she so deserves it,\\\" explained former women's marathon record holder Paula Ratcliffe.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_of_Rome\", \"score\": 0.9997525790545498, \"rank\": 0.00021077560631763622, \"text\": \"Paula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_of_Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_of_Rome\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Keely Hodgkinson ran that race with the weight of expectation on her, everyone was hanging that medal around her neck, she knew that as well.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But to execute it in that way and to block someone of the tactical level of Mary Moraa, who can really mix it up, she was just so impressive.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1012, \"enti