27\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be the start of a big, big voyage for her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Dame Denise Lewis, who won the heptathlon gold at the Sydney 2000 Olympics, said: \\\"Keely Hodgkinson was ready for it, she had to race smart.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Denise Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\"}, {\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not shake her opponents until the very end.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was so tense, but she delivered, she ran the race that suited her and ended up taking it by the scruff of the neck because she knew she had to.\\\"\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Team GB win 11th gold at Olympics and smash world record in women's team sprint  Do not miss:Serena Williams and children 'denied Paris restaurant entry' at Olympics 2024  Do not miss:Novak Djokovic gets apology from TV network after Carlos Alcaraz Olympics final  London 2012 Olympic heptathlon champion Dame Jessica Ennis-Hill added: \\\"I am literally shaking, I am blown away.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http: